    "description": "<strong>This Demo includes every important mechanic the game features. The main difference from the full release and the demo is the demo won't receive Big Updates.</strong><br><br>Welcome Fear Follower! Your mission is to earn reputation for the Cult of Fear Followers by recording evidence of our Sacred Entities. Form a team of up to 4 members to: detect, investigate, record, and review.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/9469ed5a956a26f50916fce40ab22e20.poster.avif?t=1722531814\" width=616 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/9469ed5a956a26f50916fce40ab22e20.webm?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/9469ed5a956a26f50916fce40ab22e20.mp4?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use your video camera's detection system to find the Sacred Entity... but beware! Other lesser entities roam the facility, making the mission even more dangerous.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/cb2590df9364a239df06cf69aa0a3680.poster.avif?t=1722531814\" width=616 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/cb2590df9364a239df06cf69aa0a3680.webm?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/cb2590df9364a239df06cf69aa0a3680.mp4?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Once you detect the Sacred Entity, we will show you what evidence you need in order to summon the entity. You must find 3 types of evidence, each combination specific to it's own Sacred Entity. Use your camera to record the evidence so that we may have proof of the Entity's existence.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/0a871ca09ee4329e6c3a256c35572945.poster.avif?t=1722531814\" width=616 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/0a871ca09ee4329e6c3a256c35572945.webm?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/0a871ca09ee4329e6c3a256c35572945.mp4?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>After you find all the evidence specifically needed for the Sacred Entity, you can summon it. Once summoned, you must record the Sacred Entity itself. When you record the Sacred Entity, you earn the Cult more reputation. Use the reputation you earn to buy new tools, such as evidence gatherers, that unlock new Entities to discover.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/2032f43ccaa2d1fb975ad31fbba31beb.poster.avif?t=1722531814\" width=616 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/2032f43ccaa2d1fb975ad31fbba31beb.webm?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3134270/extras/2032f43ccaa2d1fb975ad31fbba31beb.mp4?t=1722531814\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>All the footage you recorded can be reviewed on your ship's TV.<br><br><br>What're you waiting for, Fear Follower? These entities aren't going to record themselves!",
